acceptedAnswer" itemscope=3D"" itemtype=3D"https://schema.org/Answer"><div =
itemprop=3D"text">
<p>To find the perimeter of a parallelogram, add all the sides together. Th=
e following formula gives the perimeter of any parallelogram:</p>
<p>Perimeter =3D 2 (a + b)</p>
</div></div></div></section><section class=3D"faq-item" itemscope=3D"" item=
